<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Act 12:</b></font>

28
00:02:07,034 --> 00:02:10,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}Eight-Six vs. Eight-Six: A Spirited Race"</b></font>

29
00:02:07,674 --> 00:02:12,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Man, I just can't stay calm.
--Me neither.</b></font>

30
00:02:12,174 --> 00:02:14,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I have to work.</b></font>

31
00:02:14,244 --> 00:02:17,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe you can go and...</b></font>

32
00:02:18,844 --> 00:02:21,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Boss.</b></font>

33
00:02:21,554 --> 00:02:24,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just go while I'm looking the other way.</b></font>

34
00:02:24,524 --> 00:02:26,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay! Ready, Kenji?</b></font>

35
00:02:26,854 --> 00:02:28,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

36
00:02:33,194 --> 00:02:35,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If I were a little younger,</i></b></font>

37
00:02:35,694 --> 00:02:38,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I would leave work to see it, too.</i></b></font>

38
00:02:40,534 --> 00:02:42,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll be right there!</b></font>

39
00:02:47,214 --> 00:02:51,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come on, we're in a hurry!</b></font>

40
00:02:51,114 --> 00:02:53,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Look, Kenji.</b></font>

41
00:02:53,914 --> 00:02:56,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Isn't that Takumi's girl?</b></font>

42
00:02:56,654 --> 00:02:59,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, you're right.</b></font>

43
00:02:59,424 --> 00:03:02,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe she's looking for a part-time job.</b></font>

44
00:03:09,264 --> 00:03:10,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Seibu Chichibu Station"</b></font>

45
00:03:27,184 --> 00:03:29,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

46
00:03:29,354 --> 00:03:32,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Kazumi!
--Itsuki?</b></font>

47
00:03:32,524 --> 00:03:34,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why are you here?</b></font>

48
00:03:34,354 --> 00:03:37,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A lot's happened since last night.</b></font>

49
00:03:38,724 --> 00:03:42,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're the one who chose this location.</b></font>

50
00:03:44,034 --> 00:03:46,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kazumi, you guys wait here.</b></font>

51
00:03:46,464 --> 00:03:48,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But why?</b></font>

52
00:03:48,204 --> 00:03:51,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can catch a bus or a train
from here in the morning.</b></font>

53
00:03:51,644 --> 00:03:55,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If anything should happen to our cars,</b></font>

54
00:03:55,144 --> 00:03:58,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>at least you won't be stuck here.</b></font>

55
00:03:58,244 --> 00:04:00,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?! Takumi!</b></font>

56
00:04:02,484 --> 00:04:05,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you guys going to Shomaru Pass?</b></font>

57
00:04:05,824 --> 00:04:07,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You shouldn't race there!</b></font>

58
00:04:07,654 --> 00:04:10,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Pick another place!
--Be quiet, Kazumi.</b></font>

59
00:04:10,494 --> 00:04:11,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Stay out of this.</b></font>

60
00:04:11,994 --> 00:04:15,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Big brother...
--Just so you know...</b></font>

61
00:04:15,894 --> 00:04:20,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...the pass we're about to race
on is very narrow and tricky.</b></font>

62
00:04:20,734 --> 00:04:22,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll take the lead first.</b></font>

63
00:04:22,674 --> 00:04:25,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Since this is your first time,</b></font>

64
00:04:25,004 --> 00:04:28,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>we should take some precautions.</b></font>

65
00:04:28,214 --> 00:04:30,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll alternate positions</b></font>

66
00:04:30,384 --> 00:04:32,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and keep going until one pulls away</b></font>

67
00:04:32,884 --> 00:04:34,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>or passes the other.</b></font>

68
00:04:34,884 --> 00:04:37,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a sudden death race.</b></font>

69
00:04:37,054 --> 00:04:41,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If we're equally skilled,
another element will be the factor.</b></font>

70
00:04:41,694 --> 00:04:43,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Another element?</b></font>

71
00:04:43,424 --> 00:04:45,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Luck, stamina,</b></font>

72
00:04:45,224 --> 00:04:48,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>compatibility with the car... that sort of thing.</b></font>

73
00:04:48,734 --> 00:04:50,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's go.</b></font>

74
00:04:50,034 --> 00:04:52,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When we get there,
I'll turn on my hazard lights</b></font>

75
00:04:52,864 --> 00:04:54,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and we'll start.</b></font>

76
00:05:11,154 --> 00:05:12,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Takumi!</i></b></font>

77
00:05:14,594 --> 00:05:19,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Did Takumi know that</i>
<i>Kazumi would be here, too?</i></b></font>

78
00:05:25,434 --> 00:05:29,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is Shomaru Pass really that dangerous?</b></font>

79
00:05:29,034 --> 00:05:31,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's an old road.</b></font>

80
00:05:31,044 --> 00:05:33,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not that long,</b></font>

81
00:05:33,004 --> 00:05:36,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but you go uphill first,
then downhill from the middle.</b></font>

82
00:05:36,844 --> 00:05:39,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's half uphill, then.</b></font>

83
00:05:39,344 --> 00:05:41,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's not all.</b></font>

84
00:05:41,554 --> 00:05:43,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's narrow and has poor visibility,</b></font>

85
00:05:43,854 --> 00:05:46,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>which has resulted in many accidents.</b></font>

86
00:05:46,684 --> 00:05:48,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The guardrails are all rusted.</b></font>

87
00:05:48,754 --> 00:05:51,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The road's uneven and slippery.</b></font>

88
00:05:51,094 --> 00:05:54,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wataru has had two accidents there.</b></font>

89
00:05:54,934 --> 00:05:58,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He said it was a tough pass to race.</b></font>

90
00:05:58,104 --> 00:05:59,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

91
00:05:59,604 --> 00:06:01,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is Takumi's first time!</b></font>

92
00:06:01,534 --> 00:06:03,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's too risky!</b></font>

93
00:06:13,014 --> 00:06:15,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>His hazard lights! Here we go...</i></b></font>

94
00:06:15,514 --> 00:06:19,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ready? Don't crash your precious car yet.</i></b></font>

95
00:06:26,224 --> 00:06:28,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's an uphill.</i></b></font>

96
00:06:33,604 --> 00:06:35,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

97
00:06:38,444 --> 00:06:40,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I told you so.</b></font>

98
00:06:40,674 --> 00:06:42,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a great engine.</b></font>

99
00:06:42,514 --> 00:06:45,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can even stay with me on this hill.</b></font>

100
00:06:45,214 --> 00:06:48,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No need to take it easy, then!</b></font>

101
00:06:56,454 --> 00:06:59,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Good night!
--Bye! Take care.</b></font>

102
00:07:03,234 --> 00:07:06,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm sorry, Takumi.</i></b></font>

103
00:07:06,704 --> 00:07:10,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm the one who's to blame.</i></b></font>

104
00:07:10,474 --> 00:07:12,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I know that now,</i></b></font>

105
00:07:12,304 --> 00:07:14,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but I don't know what to do.</i></b></font>

106
00:07:14,714 --> 00:07:19,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>So for now, I'll try working</i>
<i>part-time like you, Takumi.</i></b></font>

107
00:07:21,984 --> 00:07:24,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm determined to change.</i></b></font>

108
00:07:36,994 --> 00:07:39,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I drive an Eight-Six</i></b></font>

109
00:07:39,034 --> 00:07:42,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>because defeating an opponent</i>
<i>with this disadvantageous old car</i></b></font>

110
00:07:42,104 --> 00:07:45,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>is so satisfying.</i></b></font>

111
00:07:45,404 --> 00:07:48,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But this time, it's different.</i></b></font>

112
00:07:48,214 --> 00:07:52,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I absolutely can't lose to another Eight-Six!</i></b></font>

113
00:07:52,244 --> 00:07:56,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I've never felt this much</i>
<i>pressure in a race before!</i></b></font>

114
00:07:56,614 --> 00:08:00,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can see the aura that</i>
<i>radiates from your Trueno!</i></b></font>

115
00:08:06,294 --> 00:08:08,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is this a good spot, Keisuke?</b></font>

116
00:08:08,994 --> 00:08:13,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The course is so narrow that
there's no other place to watch from.</b></font>

117
00:08:15,334 --> 00:08:17,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There!</i></b></font>

118
00:08:25,844 --> 00:08:28,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here we go!</b></font>

119
00:08:31,824 --> 00:08:36,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That sudden boost of power is to die for!</i></b></font>

120
00:08:43,534 --> 00:08:47,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The obsolete "boom" turbo.</b></font>

121
00:08:47,004 --> 00:08:48,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Keisuke?</b></font>

122
00:08:48,334 --> 00:08:50,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Aren't Fujiwara's Trueno and Akiyama's Levin</b></font>

123
00:08:50,844 --> 00:08:55,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>basically the same car except for
their front and tail lamp designs?</b></font>

124
00:08:55,714 --> 00:08:59,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Yeah.
--Why do they run differently, then?</b></font>

125
00:08:59,014 --> 00:09:02,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, that's because...</b></font>

126
00:09:02,114 --> 00:09:05,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I should have my brother explain it to you.</b></font>

127
00:09:05,454 --> 00:09:10,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I understand it in my head,
but I'm not good at explaining.</b></font>

128
00:09:10,124 --> 00:09:14,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Like Kenta said, the Trueno
and the Levin are like twins.</b></font>

129
00:09:14,334 --> 00:09:18,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But since their engines take
different tuning methods,</b></font>

130
00:09:18,334 --> 00:09:21,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>they've become two completely different cars.</b></font>

131
00:09:21,974 --> 00:09:26,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The method without the turbocharger
is called mechanical tuning.</b></font>

132
00:09:27,844 --> 00:09:30,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fujiwara's Trueno is that.</b></font>

133
00:09:32,344 --> 00:09:36,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His foot on the gas pedal
controls the rpm directly.</b></font>

134
00:09:36,984 --> 00:09:39,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Its instant response is its strength.</b></font>

135
00:09:39,924 --> 00:09:42,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even after entering a corner
at nearly top speed,</b></font>

136
00:09:42,924 --> 00:09:47,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>he can make further adjustments to his attack.</b></font>

137
00:09:49,034 --> 00:09:51,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Unlike with a turbo,</b></font>

138
00:09:51,234 --> 00:09:53,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>he can attack corners aggressively.</b></font>

139
00:09:53,264 --> 00:09:58,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Cars like his excel at entering corners.</b></font>

140
00:09:58,044 --> 00:10:01,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In contrast, Akiyama's Levin is a turbo.</b></font>

141
00:10:01,674 --> 00:10:05,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It may be a step slower at corners,</b></font>

142
00:10:05,244 --> 00:10:08,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but its acceleration on
straightaways covers that.</b></font>

143
00:10:09,754 --> 00:10:13,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Cars with turbos excel
at coming out of corners.</b></font>

144
00:10:13,854 --> 00:10:17,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How about the Levin's fishtailing, then?</b></font>

145
00:10:17,524 --> 00:10:20,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The "boom" turbo tends to lag,</b></font>

146
00:10:20,524 --> 00:10:22,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so once the boost pressure goes down,</b></font>

147
00:10:22,864 --> 00:10:25,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it takes time to get it back up.</b></font>

148
00:10:25,364 --> 00:10:30,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's why he keeps his foot
on the gas when exiting corners</b></font>

149
00:10:30,204 --> 00:10:33,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and controls it using counter-steer only.</b></font>

150
00:10:33,274 --> 00:10:36,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He probably mastered
that fishtailing technique</b></font>

151
00:10:36,574 --> 00:10:40,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to deal with the peculiarities of his car.</b></font>

152
00:10:40,984 --> 00:10:42,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Got it, Kenta?</b></font>

153
00:10:42,984 --> 00:10:45,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Pass racing is very complex.</b></font>

154
00:10:45,654 --> 00:10:48,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes, I get it now.</b></font>

155
00:11:45,044 --> 00:11:47,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's up with that?!</b></font>

156
00:12:03,834 --> 00:12:06,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you sure this is the place?</b></font>

157
00:12:06,234 --> 00:12:09,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, I guess so.</b></font>

158
00:12:09,574 --> 00:12:11,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's that?</b></font>

159
00:12:13,604 --> 00:12:15,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi!</b></font>

160
00:12:45,444 --> 00:12:47,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow! That's a "boom" turbo.</b></font>

161
00:12:47,814 --> 00:12:50,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That car almost looks out of control.</b></font>

162
00:12:50,914 --> 00:12:54,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's barely staying on this narrow road.</b></font>

163
00:12:54,614 --> 00:12:57,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But when he's on, he's super fast.</b></font>

164
00:12:57,954 --> 00:13:00,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's a different kind of opponent</b></font>

165
00:13:00,624 --> 00:13:03,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>who breaks all the conventional rules.</b></font>

166
00:13:07,024 --> 00:13:09,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is the second round.</i></b></font>

167
00:13:09,694 --> 00:13:12,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>From behind, I'll be observing</i></b></font>

168
00:13:12,204 --> 00:13:15,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>your undefeated Gunma-grown talent.</i></b></font>

169
00:13:20,674 --> 00:13:24,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This corner is hard to get through!</b></font>

170
00:13:27,684 --> 00:13:32,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right now, all the elements
are against Fujiwara.</b></font>

171
00:13:32,624 --> 00:13:35,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a tricky course where
he has no experience,</b></font>

172
00:13:35,924 --> 00:13:39,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and the Levin's irregular
pace breaks his rhythm.</b></font>

173
00:13:41,034 --> 00:13:42,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But more than anything,</b></font>

174
00:13:42,864 --> 00:13:44,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>he has been feeling uneasy</b></font>

175
00:13:44,704 --> 00:13:48,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>with his new and unfamiliar Eight-Six.</b></font>

176
00:13:48,974 --> 00:13:51,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's his biggest handicap.</b></font>

177
00:13:53,704 --> 00:13:57,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The bad condition of this road</i>
<i>is making my car shake!</i></b></font>

178
00:14:00,984 --> 00:14:04,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The inner edge of the road is unusable!</i></b></font>

179
00:14:04,224 --> 00:14:07,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If the tires catch it, they'll slip!</i></b></font>

180
00:14:09,494 --> 00:14:14,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't use the outer edge</i>
<i>coming out of corners, either.</i></b></font>

181
00:14:14,334 --> 00:14:19,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There's less usable area on this</i>
<i>road than there appears to be.</i></b></font>

182
00:14:23,834 --> 00:14:25,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Takumi...</i></b></font>

183
00:14:25,044 --> 00:14:29,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The suspension settings change</i>
<i>based on the engine power.</i></b></font>

184
00:14:29,844 --> 00:14:31,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>After I installed the new engine,</i></b></font>

185
00:14:31,584 --> 00:14:35,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>you kept saying you couldn't corner like before,</i></b></font>

186
00:14:35,454 --> 00:14:37,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>which is logical.</i></b></font>

187
00:14:37,854 --> 00:14:42,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The car was set up that way.</i></b></font>

188
00:14:43,854 --> 00:14:47,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Only by revving up to a</i>
<i>high rpm will you be able</i></b></font>

189
00:14:47,524 --> 00:14:50,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>to corner at a higher speed.</i></b></font>

190
00:14:52,034 --> 00:14:53,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Notice that, Takumi.</i></b></font>

191
00:14:53,734 --> 00:14:57,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Unseal the car's capabilities.</i></b></font>

192
00:15:01,974 --> 00:15:04,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What's this?</i></b></font>

193
00:15:04,484 --> 00:15:06,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Did I imagine it?</i></b></font>

194
00:15:17,494 --> 00:15:22,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The turbo is so fast that I'm kind of scared.</i></b></font>

195
00:15:22,334 --> 00:15:25,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This car is nothing like it was before.</b></font>

196
00:15:25,534 --> 00:15:28,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It needs more detailed maintenance.</b></font>

197
00:15:28,834 --> 00:15:32,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And I have to watch the
gauges while I'm racing.</b></font>

198
00:15:32,544 --> 00:15:35,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It costs money and takes effort,</b></font>

199
00:15:35,614 --> 00:15:38,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I have no regrets.</b></font>

200
00:15:38,514 --> 00:15:41,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've gained the power I was craving.</b></font>

201
00:15:41,914 --> 00:15:43,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See, Kazumi...</b></font>

202
00:15:43,584 --> 00:15:47,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...it's no good if you stop growing.</b></font>

203
00:15:47,354 --> 00:15:50,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you keep running away
from things you're bad at,</b></font>

204
00:15:50,694 --> 00:15:53,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you'll never be good at anything.</b></font>

205
00:15:53,364 --> 00:15:56,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You just have to keep searching</b></font>

206
00:15:56,034 --> 00:15:58,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and moving forward on your own two feet.</b></font>

207
00:16:00,634 --> 00:16:02,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Big brother...</b></font>

208
00:16:02,134 --> 00:16:03,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kazumi?</b></font>

209
00:16:03,804 --> 00:16:06,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, thank you.</b></font>

210
00:16:06,974 --> 00:16:08,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's warm.</b></font>

211
00:16:11,144 --> 00:16:14,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Listen, Itsuki.
--Yeah?</b></font>

212
00:16:14,414 --> 00:16:21,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't think I'll be going back to Gunma.</b></font>

213
00:16:21,154 --> 00:16:22,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So...</b></font>

214
00:16:22,994 --> 00:16:27,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...I guess this is probably good-bye for us.</b></font>

215
00:16:27,094 --> 00:16:28,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

216
00:16:34,834 --> 00:16:38,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My parents found out about
my leaving work the other day</b></font>

217
00:16:38,044 --> 00:16:41,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and are angry with me.</b></font>

218
00:16:41,674 --> 00:16:44,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But that's not the reason.</b></font>

219
00:16:44,344 --> 00:16:47,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was thinking in the car.</b></font>

220
00:16:47,014 --> 00:16:52,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I realized that I need to choose my own path.</b></font>

221
00:16:52,024 --> 00:16:54,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Because only if I choose my own path</b></font>

222
00:16:54,254 --> 00:16:58,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>can I say to myself that I was right in the end.</b></font>

223
00:17:01,394 --> 00:17:04,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My old job, and this temp job at the hotel,</b></font>

224
00:17:04,964 --> 00:17:07,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>weren't really my idea.</b></font>

225
00:17:07,004 --> 00:17:10,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll find a job myself this time.</b></font>

226
00:17:10,334 --> 00:17:12,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And I also have a small goal.</b></font>

227
00:17:15,214 --> 00:17:16,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A goal?</b></font>

228
00:17:16,644 --> 00:17:21,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll save up and get my
driver's license, like you.</b></font>

229
00:17:21,184 --> 00:17:24,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That'll be my first step towards independence.</b></font>

230
00:17:30,194 --> 00:17:33,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was wrong to think that
moving to another place</b></font>

231
00:17:33,194 --> 00:17:34,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>would solve my problems.</b></font>

232
00:17:34,934 --> 00:17:36,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to hold the steering wheel</b></font>

233
00:17:36,894 --> 00:17:40,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>instead of sitting in the passenger seat.</b></font>

234
00:17:40,704 --> 00:17:43,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to be able to run on my own,</b></font>

235
00:17:43,104 --> 00:17:46,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>without anyone's help.</b></font>

236
00:17:46,744 --> 00:17:49,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kazumi, I, uh...</b></font>

237
00:17:49,344 --> 00:17:52,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I won't go back to Gunma,</b></font>

238
00:17:52,014 --> 00:17:55,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>because I can't get my license there.</b></font>

239
00:17:55,014 --> 00:17:58,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Uh, I...</b></font>

240
00:17:59,424 --> 00:18:03,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you for everything, Itsuki.</b></font>

241
00:18:05,464 --> 00:18:07,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I...</i></b></font>

242
00:18:07,794 --> 00:18:10,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...have fallen in love with you, Kazumi.</i></b></font>

243
00:18:15,234 --> 00:18:17,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The second round!</b></font>

244
00:18:25,584 --> 00:18:27,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's getting used to it.</b></font>

245
00:18:27,914 --> 00:18:29,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

246
00:18:29,254 --> 00:18:32,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's time for the new Eight-Six to wake up.</b></font>

247
00:18:37,594 --> 00:18:40,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It did get easier to control.</b></font>

248
00:18:42,334 --> 00:18:45,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I was struggling with it just yesterday.</i></b></font>

249
00:18:47,364 --> 00:18:50,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Is it because of this power?</i></b></font>

250
00:18:51,844 --> 00:18:56,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can control it.</i></b></font>

251
00:18:56,774 --> 00:18:58,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>All right.</i></b></font>

252
00:18:58,684 --> 00:19:00,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I may just pull it off!</i></b></font>

253
00:19:03,454 --> 00:19:06,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I was planning to just</i>
<i>observe him in this round,</i></b></font>

254
00:19:06,624 --> 00:19:08,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but that won't work.</i></b></font>

255
00:19:08,354 --> 00:19:13,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's adapting to this tricky</i>
<i>course at an amazing rate.</i></b></font>

256
00:19:13,124 --> 00:19:16,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No other first-timer could race this fast here!</i></b></font>

257
00:19:16,534 --> 00:19:18,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm impressed!</i></b></font>

258
00:19:18,334 --> 00:19:20,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Racers like you do exist!</i></b></font>

259
00:19:20,664 --> 00:19:24,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't lose on my home turf!</i></b></font>

260
00:19:24,804 --> 00:19:27,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This will be a tough race!</i></b></font>

261
00:19:33,514 --> 00:19:36,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Make sure to rev up to 11,000 rpm.</b></font>

262
00:19:55,834 --> 00:19:59,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Good pass racers are the coolest.</i></b></font>

263
00:19:59,344 --> 00:20:01,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You're not bad.</i></b></font>

264
00:20:01,844 --> 00:20:05,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Your sharp technique could convince anyone.</i></b></font>

265
00:20:05,184 --> 00:20:08,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can go for broke with my Levin!</i></b></font>

266
00:20:13,424 --> 00:20:16,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I wanted excitement like this.</i></b></font>

267
00:20:16,224 --> 00:20:18,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm the luckiest man alive!</i></b></font>

268
00:20:38,914 --> 00:20:43,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>At the end of the last round,</i>
<i>I was going full blast.</i></b></font>

269
00:20:44,924 --> 00:20:47,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll finish you in this round!</i></b></font>

270
00:20:47,754 --> 00:20:49,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You're a great opponent.</i></b></font>

271
00:20:49,724 --> 00:20:53,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You've set my spirit on fire!</i></b></font>

272
00:21:19,384 --> 00:21:24,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Furikaereba itsudatte</i></b></font>

273
00:21:24,294 --> 00:21:29,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kawaranu kimi no egao ga atta</i></b></font>

274
00:21:29,564 --> 00:21:34,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Arukitsukare tachidomaru hi mo</i></b></font>

275
00:21:34,234 --> 00:21:43,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Chiisa na yorokobi no hi mo</i></b></font>

276
00:21:43,044 --> 00:21:51,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kono ryoute ni kakaekirenai</i></b></font>

277
00:21:51,624 --> 00:21:58,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ai wo oshiete kureta</i></b></font>

278
00:22:00,724 --> 00:22:07,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Atatakaku</i></b></font>

279
00:22:07,864 --> 00:22:15,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sotto yasashiku yomigaeru kaze wa</i></b></font>

280
00:22:15,544 --> 00:22:23,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ima hitori sora wo</i></b></font>

281
00:22:23,554 --> 00:22:30,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mitsumeteru boku ni hohoendeiru</i></b></font>

282
00:22:30,794 --> 00:22:38,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mada ano hi no mama no</i></b></font>

283
00:22:38,704 --> 00:22:48,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mabushisa de te wo futteiru</i></b></font>

284
00:22:51,384 --> 00:22:57,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kimi wa everlasting memory</i></b></font>

285
00:23:04,554 --> 00:23:07,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Each with their own hopes...</i></b></font>

286
00:23:07,994 --> 00:23:10,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Next on Initial D: Second Stage...</i></b></font>

287
00:23:10,864 --> 00:23:14,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The last episode: "Changing Seasons."</i></b></font>

288
00:23:14,774 --> 00:23:16,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't miss it!</i></b></font>

